{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/blueprints/blueprint/docs/adr/0001-use-gpl3-as-license.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dbe4a2ed-7852-54e6-93f7-98b4afe895b4","html":"<h1 id=\"use-gnu-gpl-as-license\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#use-gnu-gpl-as-license\" aria-label=\"use gnu gpl as license permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use GNU GPL as license</h1>\n<p>Everything needs to be licensed, otherwise the default copyright laws apply.\nFor instance, in Germany that means users may not alter anything without explicitly asking for permission.\nFor more information see <a href=\"https://help.github.com/articles/licensing-a-repository/\">https://help.github.com/articles/licensing-a-repository/</a>.</p>\n<p>We want to have all source code related to Operate First to be used without any hassle and as free as possible, so that\nusers can just <a href=\"https://fsfe.org/freesoftware/freesoftware.en.html\">execute and enjoy the four freedoms</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"considered-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#considered-options\" aria-label=\"considered options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Considered Options</h2>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>No license</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/share-your-work/public-domain/cc0/\">CC0</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\">GNU GPL</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"decision-outcome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#decision-outcome\" aria-label=\"decision outcome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Decision Outcome</h2>\n<p>Chosen option: “GNU GPL”, because this license supports a strong copyleft model.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/blueprint/blob/master/docs/adr/0001-use-gpl3-as-license.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dbe4a2ed-7852-54e6-93f7-98b4afe895b4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721"]}